  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Breakfast is served from 7am to 11am and offers a large variety of fresh food with produce from the hotel's own vegetable garden. When the weather's nice it's lovely eating on the garden terrace.</p>
<p>The hotel's restaurant is open for dinner between 7pm and 9pm serving traditional Italian and international food. You'll get a 15% discount on the <span>à</span> la carte dinner menu. There's also a small menu available for lunch. In the Summer, you can also have lunch on the terrace surrounded by the gardens. </p>
<p>There's a cosy bar area, where you can have wine, cocktails or coffee before and after dinner.</p>
<p><em>For Summer 23 bookings, one tasting dinner can be pre-booked at €38 per person. This includes a glass of prosecco with an entrée, a first course, main course and dessert with a choice.</em></p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
